      • createTileColumnPattern

        public static TileColumnPattern createTileColumnPattern(java.util.ArrayList<TileTypeEnum> filteredTypes,
                                                        int start,
                                                        int end)
        Creates a TileColumnPattern from an existing list of tile types and uses the start and end as indicies to get a sublist of filteredTypes.
        Parameters:
        filteredTypes - The list of tile types to turn into a pattern
        start - The start index to use to build a subList of filteredTypes
        end - The end index to use to build a subList of filteredTypes
        Returns:
        A tile column pattern or null if the list contained a NULL (break) tileType.

        public static int getCommonRow(Device dev)
        Finds the first row that has a populated BRAM or DSP tile to help identify tile column types. Can reliably iterate over this row and identify column types.
        Parameters:
        dev - The device of interest
        Returns:

      • genColumnPatternMap

        public static java.util.HashMap<TileColumnPattern,java.util.TreeSet<java.lang.Integer>> genColumnPatternMap(Device dev)
        Creates a map where the keys are all tile column patterns for the given device and the values are sets of occurrences/instances of those tile column patterns (represented by the the column index of the start of the pattern).
        Parameters:
        dev - The device of interest
        Returns:
        The map between tile column patterns and their respective instances.

        Parameters:

        Returns:
